article.description: — LaQuan Butler posted 19 points as Texas Rio Grande Valley beat Texas A&M-International 74-59 on Tuesday night in the season opener for both teams.
article.headline: Texas Rio Grande Valley tops Texas A&M-International 74-59
article.linkText: Texas Rio Grande Valley tops Texas A&M-International 74-59
article.story: EDINBURG, Texas -- — LaQuan Butler posted 19 points as Texas Rio Grande Valley beat Texas A&M-International 74-59 on Tuesday night in the season opener for both teams. Justin Johnson had 13 points and seven rebounds for Texas Rio Grande Valley. Marek Nelson added 10 points. RayQuan Taylor had eight rebounds. Mike Adewunmi had nine points and 10 rebounds. Greg Bowie II had 17 points for the Dustdevils. La-Quiem Walker added 12 points. Keldrick Hayes Jr had eight points, three rebounds and one steal. ------ For more AP college basketball coverage: https://apnews.com/Collegebasketball and http://twitter.com/AP--Top25 ------ This was generated by Automated Insights, http://www.automatedinsights.com/ap, using data from STATS LLC, https://www.stats.com
